      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example maintains its factory-spec Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and M-Variable differential lock. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement\u2014critical preventative maintenance for this platform. The suspension retains its sharp turn-in characteristics thanks to refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows minor road patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains robust, delivering linear power and exceptional chassis feedback.",
